# Fraud Detection & AML Analytics

This collection focuses on **Detecting financial crimes, credit card fraud, and money laundering using anomaly detection and graph-based approaches.**.

## Notebooks

- 01_credit_card_fraud_classification.ipynb
- 02_anti_money_laundering_graph_analytics.ipynb
- 03_synthetic_identity_fraud_detection.ipynb
- 04_transaction_anomaly_isolation_forest.ipynb
- 05_benfords_law_for_audit_analytics.ipynb
- 06_insurance_claim_fraud_scoring.ipynb
